ayos ka lang ba?

256
00:21:44,230 --> 00:21:45,670
Ang mga papet na espiritu ay mahirap patayin.

257
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:48,340
Ang aking espada ay kayang labanan sila.

258
00:21:49,430 --> 00:21:50,440
Pero napakarami.

259
00:21:51,260 --> 00:21:52,360
Hindi ko kayang patayin silang lahat.

260
00:21:56,780 --> 00:21:57,740
(May dapat akong gawin)

261
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:58,620
(para tulungan ang Her Grace.)

262
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:04,020
Oh mata ko.

263
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:05,830
Tahan na dyan.

264
00:22:10,020 --> 00:22:11,670
(Basta nararamdaman ko ang Glazed Pagoda,)

265
00:22:12,190 --> 00:22:13,100
(Hahanapin ko si Yan Ke.)

266
00:22:13,780 --> 00:22:15,020
(Then I can help Her Grace.)

267
00:22:42,110 --> 00:22:43,020
Sabi mo ang mga espiritu

268
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:44,150
lalaban lang sa mga kaaway ko.

269
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:46,410
Bakit pati tropa ko inaaway nila?

270
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:49,230
Bakit may pakialam ka

271
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:50,670
tungkol sa mga walang kabuluhang buhay?

272
00:22:51,780 --> 00:22:52,910
Ngayon sa larangan ng digmaan na ito,

273
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:55,670
libu-libong aura ang aking pinagpipiyestahan.

274
00:22:58,670 --> 00:23:00,710
Ang pagkatalo sa He Simu ay hindi magiging problema.

275
00:23:09,150 --> 00:23:11,260
Kapag ako ay naging Soberano,

276
00:23:12,430 --> 00:23:14,190
Bibigyan kita ng maraming tropa

277
00:23:14,580 --> 00:23:16,190
ayon sa gusto mo.

278
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:17,990
Walanghiyang halimaw ka!

279
00:23:18,390 --> 00:23:19,700
Ang lakas ng loob mong patayin ang aking mga tao!

280
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:29,110
Huwag isipin

281
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,820
pwede kang mag-rant sa harap ko

282
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:33,350
dahil lang meron ka
kapangyarihan ng Lantern.

283
00:23:43,630 --> 00:23:45,020
Ang pamamaraang ito ng paglilinang...

284
00:23:46,230 --> 00:23:47,670
Isang beses lang kita tuturuan.

285
00:23:48,990 --> 00:23:50,340
Isaisip ito.

286
00:23:54,230 --> 00:23:55,390
Ikaw ay walang iba kundi isang papet

287
00:23:55,390 --> 00:23:57,430
nagawa ko na.

288
00:24:05,430 --> 00:24:06,670
Mula ngayon,

289
00:24:07,430 --> 00:24:10,430
maglilingkod sa akin ang Spirits Lantern.

290
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:26,160
Glazed Pagoda?

291
00:24:48,340 --> 00:24:49,990
Gusto mo akong i-dissolve?

292
00:24:50,910 --> 00:24:52,670
Pero hindi papayag ang Lantern!

293
00:25:43,300 --> 00:25:44,140
Yan Ke,

294
00:25:44,740 --> 00:25:46,060
Ihahatid na kita.

295
00:26:02,780 --> 00:26:03,670
Ang iyong Grasya.

296
00:26:03,670 --> 00:26:04,510
Simu?

297
00:26:04,740 --> 00:26:05,580
Ayan ka na.

298
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:07,490
Umalis ka na o mamatay.

299
00:26:08,710 --> 00:26:09,550
Oo.

300
00:26:10,870 --> 00:26:12,150
Taksil Yan Ke,

301
00:26:13,150 --> 00:26:14,240
bilang Kanang Kamay,

302
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,700
nilabag mo ang mga Dekreto,

303
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,460
ginulo ang Void,
at sinalanta ang Mortal World.

304
00:26:18,100 --> 00:26:19,580
Ibabalik kita sa Void

305
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:20,420
at patayin ka.

306
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:28,220
Pagkatapos ay subukan ito.

307
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:40,880
Patayin mo ako dito

308
00:26:41,260 --> 00:26:42,700
o iligtas mo ang mga mortal na iyon.

309
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:43,940
Pumili ka.

310
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:45,560
Kahit ngayon,

311
00:26:46,860 --> 00:26:47,920
naglalaro ka pa

312
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,900
ganyang dirty trick.

313
00:26:49,780 --> 00:26:50,660
Paulit-ulit mong sinasabi

314
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:51,780
gusto mong maging Soberano.

315
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,730
Pero palagi kang nagtatago

316
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:55,220
at hindi man lang mangahas

317
00:26:55,220 --> 00:26:56,060
para labanan ako ng ulo.

318
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:57,900
Kahit si Bai Sanxing ay nahihigitan ka.

319
00:26:58,580 --> 00:26:59,560
Sa aking mga mata,

320
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,660
isa ka lang rebelde.

321
00:27:02,650 --> 00:27:04,480
Ngayon, bibigyan kita ng pagkakataon.

322
00:27:04,890 --> 00:27:05,900
Patayin mo ako

323
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:08,000
at ikaw ang magiging Soberano.

324
00:27:09,740 --> 00:27:11,080
Ganun na ba ako kadusta

325
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:13,630
sa mata mo?

326
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:31,860
Manatili ka kung nasaan ka.

327
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:40,100
Hindi sila mawawala

328
00:28:41,020 --> 00:28:42,100
hanggang sa Dakilang Ninuno

329
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,620
tinalo si Yan Ke

330
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:46,740
sa pinanggalingan.

331
00:29:34,620 --> 00:29:35,460
Mapapatay na sila ngayon.

332
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:36,660
Patay na sila.

333
00:29:47,540 --> 00:29:48,380
Ito ay...

334
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:50,260
Mga sundalong Liang,

335
00:29:51,340 --> 00:29:52,860
Pino ko ang iyong mga armas.

336
00:29:53,540 --> 00:29:54,660
Ngayon ay maaari mo na ring pumatay

337
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:55,500
itong mga papet na espiritu.

338
00:30:01,250 --> 00:30:02,100
Propeta,

339
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,630
dapat gumamit ka ng

340
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:05,980
ang kahanga-hangang pamamaraan na ito matagal na ang nakalipas!

341
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:44,940
Mga sundalo!

342
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:48,060
Ipaglaban natin ang ating bayan!

343
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:51,340
Patayin!

344
00:31:35,340 --> 00:31:36,180
Yan Ke,

345
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:38,740
nawala ka pagkatapos ng lahat.

346
00:31:40,060 --> 00:31:40,900
Hindi.

347
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:43,420
hindi ako natalo.

348
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:46,900
Sa nakalipas na 300 taon,

349
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:48,980
ang iyong tiwala,

350
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:51,740
pagtitiwala,

351
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,100
at closeness sa akin

352
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,580
lahat ay peke.

353
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:58,340
Siya Simu,

354
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:00,820
binigo mo ako!

355
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:04,940
Ang mayabang mong ama

356
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:07,980
tinatrato ako bilang isang sangla.

357
00:32:10,020 --> 00:32:12,980
Ginamit niya ako at iniwan.

358
00:32:13,620 --> 00:32:14,700
Ganun din kayo.

359
00:32:20,140 --> 00:32:23,140
Ang lahat ng aking mga hinahangaan ay nabigo sa akin.

360
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:25,540
Kaya kailangan kong hawakan ang kapangyarihan

361
00:32:25,540 --> 00:32:26,820
sa sarili kong mga kamay.

362
00:32:28,020 --> 00:32:29,340
Ang ayaw mong ibigay sa akin,

363
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:33,380
Ako mismo ang kukuha.

364
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:37,450
Ang lahat ng ito ay dapat na akin!

365
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:42,340
Ang mayroon ka lang ay makasariling pagnanasa.

366
00:32:43,060 --> 00:32:44,540
Ang lahat ng iyong pinagsisikapan ay walang kabuluhan.

367
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:47,460
Ibinigay ko sa iyo ang kapangyarihan na gusto mo.

368
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:49,280
Ngunit ang iyong walang sawang kasakiman

369
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:50,210
ay mahirap masiyahan.

370
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:51,230
Kaya pala naisip mo

371
00:32:51,230 --> 00:32:52,380
binigo ka ng lahat.

372
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:54,360
Tungkol naman sa Lantern...

373
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:55,730
Sa iyong mga mata,

374
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:56,960
ito ay isang pinakamataas na kayamanan.

375
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:58,520
Pero sa akin,

376
00:32:58,520 --> 00:32:59,960
parang trono lang.

377
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:02,140
Isang bagay lamang.

378
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:33,570
Dahil lang sa masasamang espiritu na katulad mo,

379
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,820
tatay ko at mga kapatid ko

380
00:33:36,420 --> 00:33:37,820
nawalan ng buhay!

381
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:39,700
Hayaan mo na.

382
00:33:40,180 --> 00:33:41,580
Hindi mo makokontrol ang Lantern.

383
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:55,300
Ikaw ang Soberano.

384
00:33:56,980 --> 00:33:58,700
Kung mawala ka,

385
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:00,460
marahil pagkatapos,

386
00:34:01,860 --> 00:34:03,180
lahat ng masasamang espiritu sa mundong ito

387
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:04,460
mawawala!

388
00:34:08,620 --> 00:34:09,460
Hindi!

389
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:12,570
Tumigil ka!

390
00:34:22,100 --> 00:34:22,940
Simu.

391
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:03,380
Hindi.

392
00:35:04,260 --> 00:35:05,100
Simu.

393
00:35:17,060 --> 00:35:17,900
(Ako...)

394
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:20,900
(Maaari na akong mamatay.)

395
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:24,900
(Hindi naman masama.)

396
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:28,300
(Hindi ko na kailangang tiisin ang kalungkutan)

397
00:35:29,260 --> 00:35:30,100
(o tiisin ang sakit)

398
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:31,820
(ng iniwan ng mga mahal ko.)

399
00:35:34,740 --> 00:35:35,580
(Ama.)

400
00:35:37,540 --> 00:35:38,380
(Ina.)

401
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:41,180
(Pupunta ako sa iyo.)

402
00:36:23,700 --> 00:36:24,540
Ang Void ay nanginginig.

403
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:25,860
Siya Simu ay nasa problema.

404
00:36:27,660 --> 00:36:28,500
I-secure natin ito.

405
00:36:28,780 --> 00:36:29,970
Ang mga espiritu ay hindi makakapasok sa Mortal World.

406
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:45,360
♪Nahuhulog na parang niyebe♪

407
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,300
Nagkaproblema si Simu.

408
00:36:46,370 --> 00:36:49,850
♪Mga kagalakan at kalungkutan ng mortal na mundo♪

409
00:36:49,850 --> 00:36:53,730
♪Tinatangay ng liwanag ng araw♪

410
00:36:54,140 --> 00:36:57,940
♪Ang mga anyo at kulay ng mortal na kaharian♪

411
00:36:58,210 --> 00:37:00,880
♪Nagtatagal para sa panandaliang sandali♪

412
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:05,360
♪Minsan nahawakan ng tumatawa na luha♪

413
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:08,750
♪Kung kaya kong mamuhay ng simple♪

414
00:37:08,750 --> 00:37:09,590
♪Para sa isang beses♪

415
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:11,840
♪Magiging panauhin ako sa isang matamis na panaginip♪

416
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,820
Iyon ang vital gate ng He Simu, hindi ba?

417
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:20,260
♪Ang bukang-liwayway at takipsilim ay sumikat at lumubog♪

418
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:24,060
♪Nananabik na magkita, pinaghiwalay pa ng tadhana♪

419
00:37:24,570 --> 00:37:28,180
♪Hayaan mo akong gumala♪

420
00:37:28,180 --> 00:37:31,820
♪Maliwanag at madilim, nang hindi lumingon♪

421
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:35,630
♪Maglakad sa kabilang pampang
kasama ang parol♪

422
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:39,760
♪Sinamahan ng kawalang-hanggan♪

423
00:37:39,970 --> 00:37:42,660
♪Habang umiikot at dumadaloy ang lahat♪

424
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:48,690
♪Mananatili man ako o umalis, mag-isa lang ako♪

425
00:38:02,780 --> 00:38:06,330
♪Habang lumilipat at nagbabago ang mga bituin♪

426
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:10,270
♪Ang isang siglo ay parang panaginip♪

427
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:14,040
♪Hayaan akong maglakbay sa kanilang lahat♪

428
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:17,730
♪Nang walang reincarnation♪

429
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:20,660
Ikaw munting langgam.

430
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,780
How dare you?

431
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:28,920
♪Maaaring tumagal ang mga sandali♪

432
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:33,600
♪Maglalaho ang pagmamahal at poot♪

433
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:36,620
umalis ka na! umalis ka na!

434
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,260
Xu.

435
00:38:43,740 --> 00:38:44,580
Nagkaproblema si Simu.

436
00:38:45,020 --> 00:38:45,860
Ayon kay Propeta,

437
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,780
hindi mawawala ang mga espiritung sundalong ito

438
00:38:47,780 --> 00:38:49,260
hanggang sa matalo si Yan Ke!

439
00:38:49,500 --> 00:38:50,860
Walang mangyayari kay Miss He!

440
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:54,660
Xu, hindi tayo makakapatay

441
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:56,100
lahat ng mga espiritung sundalong ito sa ating sarili.

442
00:38:56,420 --> 00:38:57,440
Kami na ang bahala sa kanila.

443
00:38:57,700 --> 00:38:58,970
Tulungan mo si Miss He.

444
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:00,220
Go!

445
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:12,020
Dapat kang manatiling buhay!

446
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:13,860
Oo!

447
00:39:13,860 --> 00:39:14,700
- Oo!
- Oo!

448
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,580
Maizi,

449
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:17,420
dalhin mo ako sa Simu.

450
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:19,580
Sige.

451
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:44,860
(Mag-isa lang ako,)

452
00:39:45,420 --> 00:39:47,540
(walang hanggan at walang kamatayan.)

453
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:09,500
(Ang ganda.)

454
00:40:10,540 --> 00:40:11,940
(Hindi na ako lonely.)

455
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:57,570
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

456
00:40:57,900 --> 00:41:02,150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

457
00:41:03,510 --> 00:41:08,880
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

458
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:13,780
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

459
00:41:14,870 --> 00:41:16,710
♪Biglang basag♪

460
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:34,360
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

461
00:41:34,540 --> 00:41:38,870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

462
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:45,630
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

463
00:41:45,860 --> 00:41:49,800
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

464
00:41:51,570 --> 00:41:53,460
♪Biglang basag♪

465
00:41:56,120 --> 00:41:59,280
♪Makinig, umaatungal ang lahat ng tunog♪

466
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:01,810
♪Habang ang malamig na yelo ay nagiging tides♪

467
00:42:01,810 --> 00:42:07,330
♪Ang kalungkutan ng isang siglo ay nakakatunaw ng mga pangarap♪

468
00:42:07,330 --> 00:42:10,570
♪Pagsunod sa patnubay ng tadhana♪

469
00:42:10,570 --> 00:42:15,430
♪Sa tadhana, ang ating mga sandali ay ipinagpalit♪

470
00:42:15,770 --> 00:42:18,790
♪Nagising ang puso bigla♪

471
00:42:18,790 --> 00:42:21,610
♪Panoorin ang pagbagsak ng mga paputok na parang bituin♪

472
00:42:21,870 --> 00:42:24,400
♪Ang bono na ito ay gusot sa isang thread♪

473
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:29,820
♪Ang mga makamundong pagmuni-muni ay kumukupas sa ambon♪

474
00:42:29,990 --> 00:42:33,060
♪Pahiram ng isang panandaliang tibok ng puso♪

475
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:38,120
♪Dinala mo ako sa mortal na alikabok,
hanggang sa nabighani ako sa mga alindog nito♪

476
00:42:38,330 --> 00:42:41,800
♪Ang puso ay nagising bigla♪

